{"tid":641390,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人鍾意聽Lofi-Hip Hop？","createTime":"2018-04-25T03:24:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-10T03:19:58.000Z","uid":34676,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"10678875604fbed19bc18333960c5f0f3fa47502","tid":641390,"uid":34676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T03:24:41.000Z","msg":"【什麼是 Lofi Hip Hop? 】<br />\n<br />\nLo-Fi 是「 low fidelity」的縮寫，從字面意思上看就是「低保真」，指的是由比較低等級的錄音設備製作而成的音樂，卻能產生一種獨有的、隨興而自由的音樂風格。<br />\n<br />\n一開始是因為獨立樂團大量興起，卻沒有高階的錄音設備，只能夠將創作以小規模的<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>粗糙</strong></span> DEMO 製作，用以跟他人交流。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">但演變至今，即便有高端的錄音設備，仍有人非常喜歡 Lofi 的特色，而刻意製造出又糊又乾的吉他聲、音樂失真等.....</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n做緊野聽真係一流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 基本上喺youtube上面打：full beat tape ,Lofi ...都會搵到好多，如果想發掘更多可以去soundcloud follow <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以下為24小時輪播歌單：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XDA7WSMyiro\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DXDA7WSMyiro&d=PGA6RBvujXFwYCvIkzbPhS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=af32507f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XDA7WSMyiro</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ohQPySWJToo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DohQPySWJToo&d=PGA6RBvujXFwYCvIkzbPhS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=e10fa115\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ohQPySWJToo</a><br />\n<br />\n我個人喜歡既track：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sNTdxN6Zgmw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DsNTdxN6Zgmw&d=PGA6RBvujXFwYCvIkzbPhS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=400267ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sNTdxN6Zgmw</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TdBSoy9F9NA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTdBSoy9F9NA&d=PGA6RBvujXFwYCvIkzbPhS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=89025e7a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TdBSoy9F9NA</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=juWVhhK_iDw&amp;t=38s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DjuWVhhK_iDw%26t%3D38s&d=PGA6RBvujXFwYCvIkzbPhS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=c893c2b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=juWVhhK_iDw&amp;t=38s</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0cKzCUdtRh8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0cKzCUdtRh8&d=PGA6RBvujXFwYCvIkzbPhS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=3ac85422\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0cKzCUdtRh8</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bcWhRxvk0lI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DbcWhRxvk0lI&d=PGA6RBvujXFwYCvIkzbPhS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=082b0631\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bcWhRxvk0lI</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eaR9KTknePE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DeaR9KTknePE&d=PGA6RBvujXFwYCvIkzbPhS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=377bf13a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eaR9KTknePE</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GSdYPkgCvtE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGSdYPkgCvtE&d=PGA6RBvujXFwYCvIkzbPhS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=af5e8196\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GSdYPkgCvtE</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wE7-5G6pzX8&amp;t=36s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwE7-5G6pzX8%26t%3D36s&d=PGA6RBvujXFwYCvIkzbPhS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=a778bcd4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wE7-5G6pzX8&amp;t=36s</a